{"tid":2139017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗中同盟成形？印度已邀請俄羅斯加入美國的印太戰略","createTime":"2020-08-04T04:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T04:18:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de20a6fddcc2da686f4e90e96ec363b248cdf09b","tid":2139017,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pYRJF7VXVVtc0Uz5TbzzQw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi4zNzM2MjYzNzM2MjY0/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/QLA7YqQn..9oJoFoAfBOFw--~B/aD05NzA7dz0xNDU2O3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/cmmedia.com.tw/8ccc98fce391d36522f52044fe764beb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpYRJF7VXVVtc0Uz5TbzzQw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi4zNzM2MjYzNzM2MjY0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQLA7YqQn..9oJoFoAfBOFw--~B%2FaD05NzA7dz0xNDU2O3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fcmmedia.com.tw%2F8ccc98fce391d36522f52044fe764beb&h=862abb1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度力邀俄羅斯加入美國所提出的印太戰略。長期以來，印度與俄國是實質軍事同盟，兩國經常舉辦聯合軍演。（圖片來源／俄羅斯衛星新聞網）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國所提倡的印太戰略（The Indo-Pacific Initiative）是一個國際戰略同盟，普遍被視為圍堵霸氣外露的中國。據外媒《The Print》報導，印度駐俄大使法碼（D. Bala Venkatesh Varma）已向俄國副外相莫古羅夫（Igor Morgulov）提出邀約，邀請俄羅斯加入印太戰略。<br />\n<br />\n印太戰略形同「抗中同盟」，印度與台灣並駕齊驅<br />\n<br />\n為了遏止中國侵犯印度、太平洋等週邊地區，美國提出所謂的印太戰略（The Indo-Pacific Initiative）。國內知名外交專家、遠景基金會執行長賴怡忠對此表示，美國防部在2018年6月提出的「印太戰略報告」，不只把台灣視為是在日、韓、澳、菲、泰這些美國條約同盟國之外，與新、紐、蒙古並列的夥伴；更把台灣與印度並肩，也較越、印尼、馬來西亞排名更前。<br />\n<br />\n外媒《The Print》也表示，印太戰略（The Indo-Pacific Initiative）是一個國際戰略同盟，在很大程度上被視為與中國對抗。不過，印度方面也考量到，如果俄羅斯加入其中，印太戰略將不再被視為一個單單只由美國領導的國際同盟...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qb5XQN9d3TdXfFfdM9M4KA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtoPTY2Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/cmmedia.com.tw/bcbf24f1a3497f2f972bce9c401205e0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fqb5XQN9d3TdXfFfdM9M4KA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtoPTY2Ng--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fcmmedia.com.tw%2Fbcbf24f1a3497f2f972bce9c401205e0&h=9bd40a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度總理莫迪（右）跟俄羅斯總統普丁（左）兩人私交甚篤。（圖片來源／克里姆林宮官網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F%E6%88%90%E5%BD%A2-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%B7%B2%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B0%E5%A4%AA%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5-000122450.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258A%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%259B%259F%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25BD%25A2-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2582%2580%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2595%25A5-000122450.html&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=80484f1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F%E6%88%90%E5%BD%A2-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%B7%B2%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B0%E5%A4%AA%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5-000122450.html</a>"}]}